                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Paroex<sup>®</sup> is supplied as a pink liquid in the following sizes:<br/>4 fl oz (118 ml) (NDC 52376-021-04) amber plastic bottles with child-resistant cap.<br/>16 fl oz (473 ml) (NDC 52376-021-02) amber plastic bottles with child-resistant cap, individually shrink wrapped with a dosage cup.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph/>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">STORE at 20ºC to 25ºC (68ºF to 77ºF), excursions permitted to 15ºC to 30ºC (59ºF to 86ºF) [See USP controlled room temperature].</content>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph/>
                  <paragraph>
