            <section>
               <id root="368257f3-2976-42af-8b60-4654d03332c1"/>
               <code code="42229-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="SPL UNCLASSIFIED SECTION"/>
               <title>
                  <content styleCode="italics">To open, press down while turning the cap. To seal, turn until cap clicks and is tight.</content>
               </title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="italics">
                        <content styleCode="bold">Directions for Use:</content>
                     </content> Fill dosage cup to the fill line (15 mL). Swish in your mouth undiluted for 30 seconds, then <content styleCode="bold">spit out</content>. Use after breakfast and before bedtime. Or, use as prescribed by your dentist.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="italics">
                        <content styleCode="bold">Note: </content>
                     </content>
                     <content styleCode="bold">To minimize medicinal taste, do not rinse with water immediately after use.</content>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">Rx Only.</content>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">Keep Out Of Reach Of Children.﻿</content>
                  </paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20160922"/>
            </section>
